Hubl.in Video Chat for Ubuntu Touch
-----------------------------------

An easy and free VideoChat service for video chats with up to 9 people for
free. No login required. Hubl.in is a video chat service using WebRTC
technology available in modern web browsers. The web app makes this service
easily accessible to you.

For more information about this awesome cross-platform service visit:

- https://hubl.in/
- https://github.com/linagora/hublin

This application is not affiliated with hubl.in. The hubl.in name,
associated trade marks and logos are trade marks of LINAGORA Group SA or
related entities.

